{"tid":14526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台長指近月天氣詭異 明年天氣預測或增至14天","createTime":"2016-11-30T14:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T14:18:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f832a16bf07b00d4453387f99ac9a5966e266e82","tid":14526,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"最後更新: 1130 18:38 / 建立時間 (HKT): 1130 16:51<br />\n<br />\n天文台台長岑智明透露，考慮在下年推出延伸天氣預報，向市民發放更長的天氣提示。他說，因應市民的需求，考慮在明年推出新的天氣提示，或可涵蓋至14天的天氣預測，例如天氣的走勢等，但至於用什麼形式表達則仍在計劃中。 <br />\n<br />\n10月氣溫創新高，秋季總雨量亦是有紀錄以來最高，超過1000毫米，岑智明形容為「詭異」，是極端天氣的現象。他指秋季在陽光少多雲多雨下仍錄得最高氣溫，顯示氣候變暖與夏季延長；在預測今年冬季的天氣方面，受拉尼娜現象影響，今年冬天會較乾。 <br />\n<br />\n天文台今日(30/11)推出「今日提提你」新服務，以簡潔圖像及文字，透過社交媒體平台和「我的天文台」手機應用程式，每晚會透過「我的天文台」及天文台在Twitter、微博和微信的帳戶發送，稱希望讓市民可以便捷地分享天氣和氣候新知、天文現象、百變雲圖、歷史天氣等資訊。 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161130/55985806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161130%2F55985806&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkQv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=75fea71c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161130%2F55985806&h=692c2bb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161130/55985806</a>"},{"pid":"40d04d2ecab6cce3dca83a10a02aa6b4efc00e6f","tid":14526,"uid":3936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"聽日都攪唔掂攪14日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa580ee0597e7f8d46b2ad408be7e831a5308e1","tid":14526,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽日都攪唔掂攪14日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223570ec778aecf926f44e6067318d533974f947","tid":14526,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:13:25.000Z","msg":"咩野地方預報都好，10日打後都係只供參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絕對唔可以用黎作準，只係用黎睇趨勢，<br />\n會轉暖定轉冷，黎緊有無大雨機會<br />\n（實際日子唔準，例如預測12日後有大雨，可能提早2日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但可以參考未來一星期易有大雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nBTW以香港人民智，實唔知點用7日打後既預報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大交合玩死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8e7a130b6db3131a3fd9dc9b114e3b05dea956","tid":14526,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"大交合第二日都搞唔掂啦"}]}